{"tid":950484,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"(救教)迴旋處點行先為之正確/最好?","createTime":"2018-12-21T14:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T00:35:59.000Z","uid":60860,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"824e620825bbee68e2d04799c3a377b3820b8111","tid":950484,"uid":60860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:24:59.000Z","msg":"小弟依幾日行林錦公路交匯處有個疑問<br />\n我係由大埔公路大窩段入迴旋處,打算康樂園出<br />\n到底應該一直騎外圈直到出口<br />\n定抑或行內圈,接近康樂園出口先cut出外圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7868df45cd5ec99450a231ff52749e7b5ff2c71","tid":950484,"uid":196924,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:27:25.000Z","msg":"個牌點考返黎"},{"pid":"a5f98a7fd4f980bf29c5133007e79e4b58c2020a","tid":950484,"uid":9736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7868df45cd5ec99450a231ff52749e7b5ff2c71","tid":950484,"uid":196924,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:27:25.000Z","msg":"個牌點考返黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:28:32.000Z","msg":"哈"},{"pid":"32e4ad6a84913d3ea7f70f143255ce5d6244f9aa","tid":950484,"uid":29070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:33:17.000Z","msg":"望咗面睇下有冇車出<br />\n再望右面有冇車<br />\n再望左面睇下有冇車 <br />\n再望右線有冇車/電單車鳩衝<br />\n冇就出得<br />\n出左留意右面有冇車亂Cut"},{"pid":"be0a14038efd0aab9da5dfa538ca824b08946df6","tid":950484,"uid":94789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:36:53.000Z","msg":"記住出唔到就兜多個圈<br />\n唔好硬cut諗住人地會讓<br />\n兜10個圈都好過炒車"},{"pid":"81066ae0fbe830bfe32102b35685a442e1b5c88c","tid":950484,"uid":70085,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/opmeUHu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FopmeUHu.png&h=0127dfe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最憎外圈L"},{"pid":"a198603442decb77fa3f0f990af757febc89d466","tid":950484,"uid":193893,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018